{"tid":1658673,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有兩個傻佬岩岩去左柬埔塞公幹！","createTime":"2019-10-16T14:35:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T17:06:55.000Z","uid":319055,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b4ef7fee4c23a1d43e56196653eb82b14a6ce5fc","tid":1658673,"uid":319055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T14:35:35.000Z","msg":"無錯，就係我同個同事岩岩個星期比公司send去左柬埔寨做嘢。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">咁關大家咩事呢？！冇錯，其實唔關！！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n但剛剛weekend見到香港再次18區開花，又係多人受傷被捕，但自己就好似完全置身事外，果種無力感相信呢四個月有出過埠既連登仔都會理解。<br />\n<br />\n所以我哋決定點都要做番啲嘢！! 見到之前有巴打上山下海扯光復香港旗，我哋自問冇咁把炮但都試下可唔可以成功係<em><ins>世界文化遺產之一既吳哥窟</ins></em>做到呢件事。<br />\n<br />\n於是，我哋買左黑布同顏料，前一晚先吳剛師傅上身準備好支旗。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r0FitTC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr0FitTC.jpg&h=da0f6424&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jeSMCMZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjeSMCMZ.jpg&h=d007e3ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我知道有啲巴絲覺得旅行革命好左膠，我都應同。但學資深大律師駱應淦話齋：兄弟爬山。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而且要係另一個赤柬極權加上同中共有密切關係既領土做呢件事，絕對唔係想像中咁容易，無論係自己比自己既壓力，定係現場行動方面。<br />\n<br />\n最後我地一搵到比較少人既位，就快閃hit and run。沿途有外國人對我地微笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支持，亦都有疑似強國人見到眼神對我似乎不懷好意<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。結果都未入到最靚既第三層，已經比人叫收番埋去唔好再影。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lq7s6D7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLq7s6D7.jpg&h=377a666c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rWWxyjf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrWWxyjf.jpg&h=f3d1fe78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YdBQ4q5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYdBQ4q5.jpg&h=3c2cb38b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n同樣地，如果香港人今日放棄，我地既結局只會更悽慘。到時唔好話上街表達自己訴求，連平時生活上網絡上既一言一行都要不斷自我審查，講錯一隻字可能你就會變浮屍。It&rsquo;s all or nothing.<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後，我哋已經番左香港，香港人，今個星期日同我出嚟，TST見！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t76UMFX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft76UMFX.jpg&h=6e859f9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\np.s 知我係邊個既唔好篤灰相認！我都比你知道左我係P牌啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c8c84174c911673b71c99cd20c7ba84c7a60dce","tid":1658673,"uid":88578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T14:38:05.000Z","msg":"支持手足"},{"pid":"87f8c7cc89439ac1fe80216533b00bb11a1a336c","tid":1658673,"uid":294432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T14:39:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b27021b6d8e63351ad3bed0bc073f31a9ec1ac4","tid":1658673,"uid":40165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T14:39:11.000Z","msg":"支持手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8be784cc8fda0900d470818dc845d323e40d54a1","tid":1658673,"uid":13781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T14:42:30.000Z","msg":"splendid"},{"pid":"8f7b64b01380aea9778a9ecf1a1551381044f04e","tid":1658673,"uid":201229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T14:45:56.000Z","msg":"勁"},{"pid":"cbcab5746d3acace5228d97a0ec18b1ce5ba0c66","tid":1658673,"uid":277560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T14:56:36.000Z","msg":"完全明白個種無力感! 雖然對抗爭無實際作為，但精神上有100分嘅支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n多謝你冒住被終国人打嘅危險都願意高舉口號旗幟影相<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"291e20cc9cad937b51a78eeb9cce31be0eeaecf0","tid":1658673,"uid":319055,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cbcab5746d3acace5228d97