r />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">入<span style=\"color: violet;\"> /task1</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZWmYt8Z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZWmYt8Z.png&h=b245ba88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\ntask1所顯示的25條tweets<br />\n係嚴重唔夠人<br />\n（大佬呀條條上唔到一千點搞呀？）<br />\n<br />\n最後咪撚再串錯hongkong!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6359452eac67feb7f122027196b65b53176df362","tid":1658673,"uid":40165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cbcab5746d3acace5228d97a0ec18b1ce5ba0c66","tid":1658673,"uid":277560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T14:56:36.000Z","msg":"完全明白個種無力感! 雖然對抗爭無實際作為，但精神上有100分嘅支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n多謝你冒住被終国人打嘅危險都願意高舉口號旗幟影相<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T16:46:16.000Z","msg":"其實都經歷左四個月 <br />\n有咁多義士手足付出左咁多<br />\n我哋仲要畏懼啲咩<br />\n我哋連少少既付出 抗爭精神都冇 <br />\n點對得住個個星期上前線幫我哋擋子彈既手足<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人！反抗！</span></strong>"},{"pid":"74a3546259fe7f96475e756d724181c17279f297","tid":1658673,"uid":318271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T17:06:55.000Z","msg":"Pish"}]}